<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٩١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَعَلَا}</span> ... لَغَالَبَ وَطَلَبَ العُلُوَّ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٩١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَمَّا يَصِفُونَ}</span> ... عَنْ وَصْفِهِمْ إِيَّاهُ بِالشَّرِيكِ، وَالوَلَدِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٩٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{هَمَزَاتِ الشَّيَاطِينِ}</span> ... وَسَاوِسِهِمْ، وَنَزَغَاتِهِمْ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَرْزَخٌ}</span> ... حَاجِزٌ دُونَ الرَّجْعَةِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ثَقُلَتْ مَوَازِينُهُ}</span> ... كَثُرَتْ حَسَنَاتُهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَلْفَحُ}</span> ... تَحْرِقُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَالِحُونَ}</span> ... عَابِسُونَ قَلُصَتْ شِفَاهُهُمْ، وَبَرَزَتْ أَسْنَانُهُمْ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{اخْسَؤُوا}</span> ... امْكُثُوا أَذِلَّاءَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَاتَّخَذْتُمُوهُمْ سِخْرِيًّا}</span> ... اشْتَغَلْتُمْ بِالاِسْتِهْزَاءِ بِهِمْ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْعَادِّينَ}</span> ... الحُسَّابَ الَّذِينَ يَعُدُّونَ الأَيَّامَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>